HEADWORD: Dissolver
<hw>Dis*solv"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, has power to dissolve or dissipate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thou kind <qex>dissolver</qex> of encroaching care.</q>
<rj><qau>Otway.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dissolving</ent>⟦br⟧
